Description:
File stream functions that avoid clobbering std{in,out,err}.

Files:
lib/stdio-safer.h
lib/fopen-safer.c
m4/stdio-safer.m4

Depends-on:
unistd-safer

configure.ac:
gl_STDIO_SAFER

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += stdio-safer.h fopen-safer.c

Include:
"stdio-safer.h"

Maintainer:
Paul Eggert, Jim Meyering

